            {"question": "When is it appropriate to negotiate salary?", "options": ["During the first interview", "After receiving a job offer", "Before applying", "Never — accept whatever is offered"], "correct_index": 1, "explanation": "Salary negotiation is most appropriate after receiving an offer, when the employer has demonstrated strong interest in you."},
            {"question": "What should you do after a job interview?", "options": ["Forget about it and move on", "Send a thank-you email within 24 hours", "Call the interviewer multiple times", "Post about it on social media immediately"], "correct_index": 1, "explanation": "A prompt thank-you email reiterates interest, references specific discussion points, and leaves a professional impression."},
