            {"question": "What is the difference between a CV and a resume?", "options": ["They are exactly the same", "A CV is comprehensive (academic history), while a resume is concise (1-2 pages, tailored)", "A CV is for freshers, resume is for experienced", "A resume is longer than a CV"], "correct_index": 1, "explanation": "A CV is a comprehensive document covering full academic/professional history; a resume is a concise, tailored 1-2 page summary."},
