            {"question": "What is the Tuckman model of team development?", "options": ["Plan, Execute, Review, Repeat", "Forming, Storming, Norming, Performing", "Hire, Fire, Rehire, Retire", "Analyse, Design, Develop, Test"], "correct_index": 1, "explanation": "Tuckman's model describes team development stages: Forming (meeting), Storming (conflict), Norming (cohesion), Performing (high productivity)."},
